  "description": "Genetic data consisting of &gt;100,000 single nucleotide polymorphisms\n (SNPs) collected using genotype-by-sequencing, from 137 drug-type\n Cannabis samples from the Netherlands. This genetic data along with\n terpene and cannabinoid content data collected\n with GC-FID, was used to analyze Cannabis labelling and\n to perfom a genome-wide association study.",
